news: [New release v0.100, contribution by @DelvinBa] A vuln report opens now on scan, therefore review and share the detected payloads more easily on bug bounty and CVE platforms
[Contribute] Injection strategies can be missing or improved for common engines like SQLite or H2, contribute and also add a Star to GitHub at https://github.com/ron190/jsql-injection
[Test reports] Auto-generated reports are now published in the wiki, review Maven site and reports at https://ron190.github.io/jsql-injection/site/index.html
